english:
Vittala panduranga ||

Shankhachakradhara vaijayanti dhara
pitambharadhara govardhanoddhara
tulasimale shobhitagala
garudagamana hari pankajanabha
ho vittalayere pandariraya vittala yere pandariraya ||vittala||

Mastakalinga swaroopa linga
roopabhanga sajjana Sangha
yadukula tilaka manmatajanaka
patitapavana deenadayalu
vittalayere pandariraya vittala yere pandariraya ||vittala||
vittala vittala jaijai vittala
vittala vittala srihari vittala

Tribhuvana roopa vishwa swaroopa
bhavabhaya tapa harisi papa
rukmini kanta roopa ananta
janani janaka tuja màvakalena
vittalayere pandariraya vittala yere pandariraya ||
Vittala vittala jai jai vittala
vittala vittala sri hari vittala

Chandrabhage teeri ubhavitevari
karakataavari ranga shilevari
jagadodhaara vedoddhara
bhaktasagara pandarapura
ho vittala yere pandariraya vittala yere pandariraya||
vittala panduranga vittala panduranga
